      <title>斗志昂扬的工作室老板助力腾讯实现全球化游戏雄心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/scrappy-studio-boss-feeds-tencent-s-lofty-global-game-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[十年前，腾讯控股有限公司旗下的趣趣工作室濒临倒闭。如今，这家拥有 1,600 名员工的工作室及其负责人张恩佐已成为这家中国娱乐公司打造国际热门作品雄心的核心人物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/scrappy-studio-boss-feeds-tencent-s-lofty-global-game-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美光赢得芯片业务，宏盟集团与 Interpublic 合并 | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-10/bloomberg-technology-12-10-2024-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 讨论了美光科技获得美国商务部奖励的巨大胜利。我们还采访了宏盟集团和 Interpublic Group 的首席执行官，他们宣布合并，创建了世界上最大的广告公司。此外，勒索软件的兴起如何揭示了投资网络安全的最佳机会。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-10/bloomberg-technology-12-10-2024-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:46:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Adobe 的 AI 视频推广落后，而 OpenAI 推出了 Sora</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/adobe-ai-video-rollout-lags-behind-openai-sora-launch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Adobe 公司推出其 AI 视频产品的速度比 OpenAI 的竞争对手 Sora 服务慢得多，这引发了人们对这家创意软件公司落后的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/adobe-ai-video-rollout-lags-behind-openai-sora-launch</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:38:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 向购物用户支付费用，以提升其应用下载量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/tiktok-pays-its-users-to-shop-if-they-boost-app-downloads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok 向用户提供数百美元的奖励，让他们花时间在应用上，邀请朋友加入并在 TikTok Shop 上购买产品，以期在美国可能被禁之前尽快扩大业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/tiktok-pays-its-users-to-shop-if-they-boost-app-downloads</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:19:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被罢免的首席执行官计划重返 Grover，以结束可能的股权蒸发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/ousted-ceo-plots-return-to-end-possible-equity-wipeout-at-grover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的设备租赁初创公司格罗弗 (Grover) 的创始人格罗弗 (Grover) 一年前被迫离开公司，目前正试图通过对抗可能抹去投资者股权价值的重组来东山再起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/ousted-ceo-plots-return-to-end-possible-equity-wipeout-at-grover</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 20:16:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果的下一代超级智能手表将能够通过卫星发送短信</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/apple-plans-apple-watch-ultra-3-next-year-with-satellite-texting-and-5g</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司计划在 2025 年为其智能手表引入卫星连接，并正在加紧开发血压功能，以吸引徒步旅行者和注重健康的消费者升级他们的设备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/apple-plans-apple-watch-ultra-3-next-year-with-satellite-texting-and-5g</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 19:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>激进分子威胁迫在眉睫，Tinder Parent Match 面临高标准转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/match-faces-high-bar-for-turnaround-as-activist-threat-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Match Group Inc. 周三召开的首次投资者会议备受期待，活动人士和分析师正在等待该公司推出具体计划，以扭转其旗舰约会应用 Tinder 用户数量持续下滑的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/match-faces-high-bar-for-turnaround-as-activist-threat-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 18:55:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Willow 量子芯片取得突破，Alphabet 股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/alphabet-climbs-following-breakthrough-with-willow-quantum-chip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谷歌母公司 Alphabet Inc. 周一宣布通过使用 Willow 量子芯片在量子计算方面取得重大进展，分析师对此表示赞赏，该公司股价创下 4 月份以来的最大单日涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/alphabet-climbs-following-breakthrough-with-willow-quantum-chip</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 15:50:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美光获 62 亿美元芯片订单，以刺激工厂扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/micron-gets-6-2-billion-chips-award-to-spur-plant-construction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府已达成最终协议，将从旨在促进美国半导体制造业发展的计划中向美光公司提供近 62 亿美元的补贴，使资金开始流向爱达荷州和纽约州的工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/micron-gets-6-2-billion-chips-award-to-spur-plant-construction</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 15:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>甲骨文公布令人失望的增长业绩，股价今年跌幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/oracle-posts-lackluster-growth-denting-cloud-unit-enthusiasm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软件巨头甲骨文公司公布季度营收表现不尽如人意，其股价随后出现一年来最大跌幅，令近期因对该公司蓬勃发展的云计算业务的热情而将该股推至历史新高的投资者感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/oracle-posts-lackluster-growth-denting-cloud-unit-enthusiasm</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 21:17:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
